    <div class="prose" style="max-width:72ch">
      <h3>First-bag satisfaction guarantee</h3>
      <p>On Roccia, Sorpresa, and Selezione, if your first bag is not right for you, we will send a different one — free. We would rather help you find your coffee than win an argument.</p>
      <h3>Offerta is different — sold as-is</h3>
      <p>Offerta lots are good coffee approaching the edge of their freshness window, priced down honestly. They carry a modified guarantee: material defects only, with the freshness window disclosed at purchase. No exchanges for age-related palate preferences.</p>
      <h3>Damage replacement</h3>
      <p>If a bag arrives damaged, tell us and we will replace it.</p>
      <h3>Freshness window</h3>
      <p>We airfreight coffee freshly roasted in Italy in superior quality, sealed packages and ship them to you with ample time to enjoy. Every package has a roast date, and we recommend that you consume the coffee within 60 days of the roast date for maximum enjoyment.</p>
      <h3>Our no-waste pledge</h3>
      <p>Coffee that passes its freshness window is removed from sale and donated to Feeding Tampa Bay. We do not discount our way out of waste; we give it away.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

