<!-- ============================== FAQ ============================== -->
<div class="page" id="page-faq">
  <main class="ci-main">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="showPage('home')">Back to home</button>
    <div class="section-head" style="margin-top:0"><p class="eyebrow">Questions</p><h2>FAQ</h2></div>
    <div class="prose" style="max-width:72ch">
      <h3>Do you sell ground coffee?</h3>
      <p>No. Everything is whole bean, because that is what our roasters seal in valve bags at origin. Grind fresh just before you brew.</p>
      <h3>Do you roast the coffee?</h3>
      <p>No. We import and curate; the roasters roast. We never roast, blend, or repackage.</p>
      <h3>How do subscriber discounts work?</h3>
      <p>An active Roccia subscription gives 10% off Roccia, Sorpresa, and Selezione (Founding Members — the first 222 subscribers at launch — receive 12% for life). Offerta and Bottega are never discounted. On your very first order, a one-time first-purchase 5% stacks on top — so a new subscriber's first order is 15% off eligible shelves.</p>
      <h3>Is there a promo code box at checkout?</h3>
      <p>No. Any discount you have earned applies through a personal link or automatically when you are signed in — there is no code field to hunt for.</p>
      <h3>How fresh is the coffee?</h3>
      <p>Best within 60 days of the roast date, which we always show. Sorpresa Tours are assembled on-demand so every bag ships fresh.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

